# Design semantic cache on Cachex

## Description
Design a semantic response cache built on Cachex that stores LLM responses keyed by semantic meaning rather than exact text match. This enables cache hits for semantically similar queries.

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Create `PagServer.Cache.SemanticCache` module wrapping Cachex
- [ ] Define cache entry structure: query_embedding, response, metadata, created_at
- [ ] Configure dedicated Cachex cache (`:semantic_response_cache`)
- [ ] Add LRU eviction policy with configurable size limit
- [ ] Implement cache key generation from normalized query
- [ ] Add cache stats tracking (hits, misses, evictions)
- [ ] Tests pass
- [ ] Lint passes

